```plantuml
@startuml GoogleCloudPlatform_analytics-componentized-patterns

actor User

participant "BigQuery ML" as BQML
participant "Kubeflow Pipelines" as KFP
participant "Cloud Storage" as CS
participant "AI Platform Prediction" as AIP
participant "Vertex AI" as VAI
participant "Google Ads API" as GAAPI
participant "Dataflow" as DF
participant "Custom Container" as CC
participant "Data Studio" as DS

User -> BQML: Request model training
activate BQML
BQML -> DF: Prepare and transform data
activate DF
DF -> BQML: Return transformed data
deactivate DF
BQML -> BQML: Train and evaluate model
BQML -> CS: Export model artifacts
deactivate BQML
CS -> AIP: Deploy model for prediction
activate AIP
AIP -> User: Provide prediction results
deactivate AIP

User -> KFP: Initiate pipeline
activate KFP
KFP -> BQML: Train model using pipeline
KFP -> AIP: Deploy model using pipeline
KFP -> VAI: Deploy model using Vertex AI
deactivate KFP

User -> GAAPI: Activate marketing campaign
activate GAAPI
GAAPI -> User: Return campaign metrics
deactivate GAAPI

User -> DS: Visualize data and results
activate DS
DS -> User: Display dashboard
deactivate DS

User -> CC: Request real-time recommendation
activate CC
CC -> CS: Access ScaNN index
CC -> User: Provide real-time results
deactivate CC

@enduml
```